{"tid":1354054,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"派$8000","createTime":"2019-07-23T05:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T08:28:56.000Z","uid":159916,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"26f5131a3e141a47d3be280341ce7f10c652c6c9","tid":1354054,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T05:24:22.000Z","msg":"至2018年年中，二十歲以上人口有 629萬。<br />\n若向每個成年人派$8000，咁至少要用503.2億。<br />\n<br />\n相關數字：<br />\n香港警務處今個財政年度預算有206.8億、監警會0.959億、消防處 71.6億。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：派$8000、警隊減人工<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：增加消防處、監警會預算、警隊減人工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe 2019-2020 Budget Estimate<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/estimates.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.budget.gov.hk%2F2019%2Fchi%2Festimates.html&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=0bf22a51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.budget.gov.hk/2019/chi/estimates.html</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Monthly Digest of Statistics<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp20.jsp?productCode=B1010002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Fhkstat%2Fsub%2Fsp20.jsp%3FproductCode%3DB1010002&d=54aT4HSs0KTXNgMEhauAQSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=5a64b8cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/hkstat/sub/sp20.jsp?productCode=B1010002</a>"},{"pid":"a826cc8685f98989462fe34504418ad37a1c42fa","tid":1354054,"uid":161988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:37:50.000Z","msg":"支持取消警隊，將警隊既支出撥曬去派比市民"},{"pid":"5c586e46f256fb0018a0c63c6926d45d6b8cf865","tid":1354054,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d2a8c52536b14f6a05c14fe2b860d6077b444d","tid":1354054,"uid":41525,